&lt;p class=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;至於香港癌症第三位殺手肝癌，雖然早期肝癌可以手術切除，消融術或肝移植治癒；但大部分（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;60%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;）病人有症狀時已為晚期，入侵了主靜脈或已轉移肝外，只可靠藥物延續生命。一項於&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;名晚期肝癌病人的研究顯示（包括&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;名香港人），當中七成患者有肝外轉移；於傳統治療包括標靶藥物索拉菲尼失效後，應用抗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;PD-1 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;治療，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;名患者腫瘤明顯縮小，其中兩名患者腫瘤更完全消失，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;其&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;名患者在&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;個月內的短期&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;JA&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;治療&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;後已有明顯反應，而且反應在停藥後仍持續長時間。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: 細明體; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;香港衛生處已批准使用之抗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;PD-1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: 細明體; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;包括鈉武單抗（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;Nivolumab&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: 細明體; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;）及派姆單抗（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;Pembrolizumab&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: 細明體; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: