&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 6px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20.7px;&quot;&gt;憑票免費入場，名額有限，先到先得&lt;/p&gt;
