&lt;div style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.cancerinformation.com.hk/ufiles/Image/a4.jpg&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;302&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;卵巢癌女患者佩佩，如何在與癌魔作戰時從孤單中找到支持，再在康復路途中幫助同路人，帶出助人自助的精神。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
