&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/ufiles/Image/jcecc-1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;650&quot; height=&quot;934&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;由癌症資訊網、羅氏大藥廠香港有限公司及香港醫護聯盟合辦，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;2016&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;日晚舉行的「認識肺癌」專題健康講座，邀得荃灣港安醫院臨床腫瘤科專科醫生區兆基講解肺癌的症狀及最新治療方法。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/ufiles/Image/DSC05158-2.JPG&quot; width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;695&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&amp;#10;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&amp;#10;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;區醫生指出，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;肺癌&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;主要&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;分為「非小細胞癌」及「小細胞癌」，&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;主要可預防病因是吸煙，其他原因包括二手吸煙，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;接觸致癌物質如石棉煤，鋁，油漆，砷，鎘，鉻，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;鎳&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;等，接觸輻射如&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;氡&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;氣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;钚&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;等&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;。但&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;在香港，&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;90&lt;/span&gt;％的女性肺癌患者和&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;％的男性肺癌患者從未吸煙，其原因仍在研究中&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&amp;#10;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;區&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;醫生表示，很多早期肺癌缺乏明顯症狀，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;約&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;60&lt;/span&gt;％的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;患者在確診時已屆晚期。肺癌的症狀包括持續咳嗽、肺部反覆感染、痰中帶血及胸部不適、肺積水及呼吸短促等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;如果轉移&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;至&lt;/span&gt;其他遠處器官如肝，骨，腦，肺，腎上腺，淋巴結等，則會出現相應症狀如腹脹，骨痛，呼吸困難，癲癇，&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;肢體&lt;/span&gt;無力，頸部腫漲或有硬塊等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;區醫生指出，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;肺癌的治療方法主要視乎患者的年齡、身體狀況、癌細胞的種類及基因變化、位置和大小，以及擴散程度。早期肺癌以外科手術為主導&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;但&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;由於其他醫學疾病或年老，一些患者不適合手術。 在這種情況下，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;高精度立體定向放射治療&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;(high precision stereotactic body radiotherapy)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;會是根治治療的一種選擇。放射治療也可以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;舒緩患者的症狀，例如骨轉移或腦轉移所引起的疼痛和不適；化學治療&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;乃&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;利用抗癌藥物殺死癌細胞，常見的副作用包括脫髮、血球數量降低、抵抗力下降、食慾不振、手足麻痹、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;腹瀉&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;或便秘等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family:細明體;&amp;#10;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&amp;#10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;區醫生稱，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;在香港，約&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;50&lt;/span&gt;％腺癌患者&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;帶有&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;EGFR&lt;/span&gt;基因突變，而現時針對這類肺癌的標靶藥有「吉非替尼」（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Gefitinib&lt;/span&gt;）、「厄洛替尼」（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Erlotinib&lt;/span&gt;）及「吉非替尼」（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Afatinib&lt;/span&gt;），能&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;抑制癌細胞生長，從而減少或延緩癌細胞增生。標靶藥物對人體正常細胞影響較少，故副作用相對化療輕微，常見副作用為皮膚反應及腸胃反應，大部分並不嚴重及可用治療控制。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&amp;#10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;至於嶄露頭角的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;免疫檢&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;查&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;點抑製&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;劑&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;(immune check point inhibitors)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;治療&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;，乃利用患者本身的免疫機制來對抗癌細胞，喚醒&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;人體免疫系統中沉睡的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;細胞，使其重新認出並攻擊癌細胞，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;雖然可能&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;MS Mincho&amp;quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;在小部份病人身上引起嚴重的自身免疫性副作用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt; 但其&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;普遍副作用是較輕微的，&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;可用於特定類別的患者，特別是具有陽性&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;PDL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;-1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;測試的癌類&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: red; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:&amp;#10;inter-ideograph;text-indent:-6.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.5&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;同時，在癌症的分子診斷方法中也有重大突破&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;液體活驗技術&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt; (liquid biopsy) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;比&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(16, 19, 26);&quot;&gt;傳統組織活檢&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(16, 19, 26);&quot;&gt;(tissue biopsy) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(16, 19, 26);&quot;&gt;更&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;方便&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;較少侵入性和創傷性&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;並可用於重複測試&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;監測癌病和&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;shorttext&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;檢測耐藥性的基因變化&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-weight:&amp;#10;bold&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:&amp;#10;inter-ideograph;text-indent:-6.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.5&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:&amp;#10;inter-ideograph;text-indent:-6.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.5&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;總括而言，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;早期肺癌仍有根治機會，即使晚期肺癌，倘患者接受適當的治療，仍可與癌共存，帶病延年。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 細明體;&quot;&gt;患者宜積極面對疾病，與醫生保持良好溝通，充分了解不同療法的風險或副作用，共同商討最合適的治療方案。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:&amp;#10;inter-ideograph;text-indent:-6.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.5&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
