&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.fringebacker.com/media/uploads/ckeditor/4b77ba272d22402caa22ceb02cef8af7/2017/10/11/%E6%87%B7%E6%84%9B%E6%9C%83_aQ5rl6XcTPi5QyBYS_+dvw_650.jpg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;TAKE﹕懷愛會 Project Care Biking 兒童單車計劃&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;近年，本會喜獲單車義工隊的協助，積極為兒童舉辦連續性的單車訓練及活動，從而建立兒童的自信心、抗逆力、毅力、社交能力、興趣和身體及精神健康，更鼓舞的是我們有機會陪伴兒童衝出香港，前往國內、台灣騎單車，甚至是騎單車環台圓夢！感恩過去有義工們的愛同行，及獲各界人士和團體捐助支持，活動方能順利完成，且帶給兒童不一樣的回憶，加添他們正能量去面對生活中的挑戰！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;感謝癌症資訊網今次為我們單車服務籌募活動費用，支持我們的孩子繼續實現每一個單車夢！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;我們的故事 @ 懷愛會&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;「懷愛會」&lt;/strong&gt;於1981年成立，服務對象為4-18歲，因家庭遇上困難暫時無法提供適當照顧之兒童。宿舍設有5所兒童之家提供24小時兒童住宿照顧服務，每所均有8個宿位，供男女童各4名居住。入住兒童的健康、學業、社交、情緒及行為均會獲得適當的照顧，並會接受正規的學校教育。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;本會亦為兒童提供有益身心之活動，以發展其潛能和興趣。透過家舍家長的關懷和照顧，讓兒童過着家庭模式的生活，享受「家」的溫暖，直至他們可以與家人團聚或被安排到可作長期居住的地方。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.fringebacker.com/media/uploads/ckeditor/4b77ba272d22402caa22ceb02cef8af7/2017/10/12/bike2_YHL644T6TVK5YWUIf6GSTQ_650.jpg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h1 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;​期望籌募經費$300,000&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; background: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;PLAN A :&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;為45位小朋友籌募台灣騎單車的旅費 (每位約需$7,000)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; background: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;PLAN B﹕ 購買單車及維修保養﹐頭盔安全裝備﹐補給食物及用品&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;電郵﹕&amp;nbsp;pcsto@projectcare.com.hk&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.fringebacker.com/media/uploads/ckeditor/4b77ba272d22402caa22ceb02cef8af7/2017/10/11/IMG-20161118-WA0014_Q7KC1rObR6a__x7WD054mg_650.jpg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;GIVE﹕8位抗癌勇士騎車環台﹐為懷愛會兒童單車計劃籌款&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;與死神擦身而過, 幸運的我們, 生命得以延續, 如何為第二人生賦予新意義?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;8位癌症康復者, 挑戰環台騎車, 風雨的路上,堅持勇往直前,信念只有一個 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;生命影響生命&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;是次籌款希望為&amp;lt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;懷愛會&amp;gt; -Project Care biking&lt;/strong&gt;單車計劃籌募活動經費﹐ 為一班需要關愛的小朋友提供單車服務，藉以增強兒童的自信心、抗逆力、毅力、社交能力、興趣和身體及精神健康。透過大家的捐助支持，他們就能拉緊自己與夢想的距離﹐ 加添他們正能量去面對生活中的挑戰！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;我們的故事 @ 香港不倒騎士&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;「香港不倒騎士」&lt;/strong&gt;於2016年7月成立﹐是一群香港癌症康復者(同路人)組織的單車群組。互相鼓勵同路人學習安全騎車﹐ 透過單車運動推廣運動抗癌。本群組透過台灣抗癌協會舉辦的「不倒騎士」台灣環島單車活動感染﹐並由癌症資訊網支持建立。運動抗癌﹐一起踏出踩虹﹗&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.fringebacker.com/media/uploads/ckeditor/4b77ba272d22402caa22ceb02cef8af7/2017/10/13/2017%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%92%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB(fb)_wolhHJZEQ8yycq3r0XxwRw_650.jpg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.fringebacker.com/media/uploads/ckeditor/4b77ba272d22402caa22ceb02cef8af7/2017/10/13/2017%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%92%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1(8)_tkqc2eZvR16VySBNOFEMqw_650.jpg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;單車-心連心&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;8位癌症康復者, 於11月5-14日挑戰騎車環台10天1100公里。 除了挑戰自己﹐也想表達幸福不是必然﹐能夠幸運康復﹐更可以追求夢想﹐都是因為曾經得到家人朋友﹐醫護及社會人士幫助和愛護﹗&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;當我們努力準備環台練車的時候﹐偶然知道了懷愛會兒童單車計劃﹐聽到這些有困難的小朋友得到愛心單車隊義工幫助和關愛﹐教懂他們踏單車﹐並且陪伴這些小朋友出國騎車﹐有機會見識世界﹐透過踏單車建立自信和正能量﹐我們被受深深感動﹗單車運動除了有益身心﹐也建立自信和毅力﹐這群缺乏家庭關顧的小朋友十分需要鼓勵和關愛。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;&gt;8位癌友代表希望透過騎車環台籌款﹐將愛傳送給這一群被需要的小朋友﹐希望善長能夠資助他們達成單車夢​﹐一起感受踏單車的快樂﹗&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

